Package: iPRSue
Title: Individual Polygenic Risk Score Uncertainty Estimation
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Dovini", "Jayasinghe", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), email = "dovini.jayasinghe@mymail.unisa.edu.au"), person("Hong", "Lee", role = c("aut", "cph"), email = "hong.lee@unisa.edu.au"))
Description: Provides tools for estimating uncertainty in individual polygenic risk scores (PRSs) 
    using both simulation-based and analytical methods. These methods help quantify variability 
    in PRS estimates for both binary and quantitative traits.
URL: https://github.com/DoviniJ/iPRSue
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
Imports:
    data.table,
    bigstatsr,
    logistf,
    stats
LazyData: true

